    &kp KP_N0   &kp KP_N1   &kp KP_N2   &kp KP_N3   &kp KP_MULTIPLY &trans      &kp PG_UP   &kp CAPS    &kp PG_DN   &trans
                                        &trans      &trans          &mo ADJ     &kp LSHFT     
